title: Rattlers (1976, Thriller) Venom strikes : The Mojave’s most feared Predators Awakens

sources.title: Rattlers (1976, Thriller) Venom strikes : The Mojave’s most feared Predators Awakens
sources.description:
They're waiting to slither you!
Herpetologist Dr. Tom Parkinson and photographer Ann Bradley race against time to uncover the truth behind a swarm of hyper-aggressive rattlesnakes terrorizing a desert town. As the snakes close in and the corrupt Colonel Stroud turns violent, the duo must fight to survive and expose the deadly secret.

Original title: Rattlers (1976)

Director: John McCauley
Writers: Jerry Golding, John McCauley

Main cast:
Sam Chew Jr. - Dr. Tom Parkinson
Elisabeth Chauvet - Ann Bradley
Dan Priest - Colonel Stroud
Ron Gold - Captain Delaney

Genres: Horror, Thriller
Release date: April 23, 1976
Filming location: Mojave Desert, California
